{"title":"使用Hexo+Github搭建自己的个人网站","slug":"使用Hexo+Github搭建自己的个人网站","date":"2018-06-08T15:56:23.519Z","updated":"2018-06-08T23:01:03.506Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/使用Hexo+Github搭建自己的个人网站.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"前言经过自己探索，笔者终于搭建好了自己的个人主页，过程是蛮艰辛的，在这里特地和大家分享一下自己的经验。<br>","covers":["http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-403c6d5f3e68592a.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/600","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-1e407777d0914855.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/600","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-213285023e42fafb.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/600","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-0e2b67104011707b.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/600","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-d40984d6b0bfbfe4.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-809553f7a8249db5.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/600","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-d51bb15bcb0bc988.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-72ec131f54699008.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-49998d58f9c89064.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-8d869a464a366100.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-eaf24669105f7742.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240","https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-7ac45e17bae67bd6.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240"],"content":"<hr>\n<h2 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h2><p>经过自己探索，笔者终于搭建好了自己的个人主页，过程是蛮艰辛的，在这里特地和大家分享一下自己的经验。<br><a id=\"more\"></a><br><img src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-403c6d5f3e68592a.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/600\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"第一步-安装git\"><a href=\"#第一步-安装git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第一步 安装git\"></a>第一步 安装git</h3><p><a href=\"https://git-for-windows.github.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Git下载地址</a><br>安装过程较为简单没有难度一路默认即可,安装好了之后可以进行下一步。</p>\n<h3 id=\"第二步-安装Node-js\"><a href=\"#第二步-安装Node-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第二步 安装Node.js\"></a>第二步 安装Node.js</h3><blockquote>\n<p>Node.js是一个Javascript运行环境(runtime environment)，发布于2009年5月，由Ryan Dahl开发，实质是对Chrome V8引擎进行了封装。Node.js对一些特殊用例进行优化，提供替代的API，使得V8在非浏览器环境下运行得更好。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">node.js下载地址</a><br><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-1e407777d0914855.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/600\" alt=\"\"><br>此处建议大家选择第二个来下载。</p>\n<h3 id=\"第三步-安装hexo\"><a href=\"#第三步-安装hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第三步 安装hexo\"></a>第三步 安装hexo</h3><p>1<em>、利用 npm 命令即可安装。在任意位置点击鼠标右键，选择cmd命令窗口<br>2、输入命令：npm install -g hexo<br>**\\</em>注意这里必须使用命令-g否则或导致命令无法识别<strong> 这也是我当时踩过的坑。</strong><br><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-213285023e42fafb.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/600\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"第四步：初始化Hexo\"><a href=\"#第四步：初始化Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第四步：初始化Hexo\"></a>第四步：初始化Hexo</h3><p>1、创建文件夹</p>\n<p>2、在Hexo文件下，右键运行cmd，输入命令：hexo init</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-0e2b67104011707b.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/600\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>3、在_config.yml,进行基础配置</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-d40984d6b0bfbfe4.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>其中可以在这里<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">浏览更多主题</a>，然后在Hexo文件夹下 Git Bash</p>\n<p>输入命令：git clone <a href=\"https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next/themes/next（next为主题名字），来获得更多主题\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next/themes/next（next为主题名字），来获得更多主题</a></p>\n<p>4、本地浏览博客</p>\n<p>  分别输入 如下命令：</p>\n<pre><code>  hexo g\n\n  hexo s\n\n这里有[更多hexo常用命令](https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000002632530)\n</code></pre><p><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-809553f7a8249db5.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/600\" alt=\"Snipaste_2018-06-08_23-25-33.png\"></p>\n<p>  在浏览器输入：localhost：4000 ，就可以进行访问，但有时不能访问的情况下要进行更改端口号打开配置文件地址如下<img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-f6e575ab8b4761e9.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\n\"><br><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-d51bb15bcb0bc988.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\"><br>网站的效果图如下<img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-8c03ae345cf5d94d.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>5、写文章</p>\n<p>在E:\\Hexo\\source_posts文件下，新建.md文件就可以写文章</p>\n<p>Md语法参考我的另一篇文章<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/writer#/notebooks/26353195/notes/29190014\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MarkDown简单入门</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"五、部署到Github上\"><a href=\"#五、部署到Github上\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、部署到Github上\"></a>五、部署到Github上</h3><p>1、申请Github账号，（注意别忘了进行账号邮箱验证）</p>\n<p>2.new repository</p>\n<p>然后点击</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-72ec131f54699008.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-49998d58f9c89064.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\"><br><strong>注意严格按照上边的形式写 你得用户名.github.io</strong></p>\n<p>3、在_config.yml进行配置<br><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-8d869a464a366100.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>4、安装<a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-deployer-git\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo-deployer-git</a>自动部署发布工具</p>\n<pre><code>npm install hexo-deployer-git  --save\n</code></pre><p>5、发布到Github</p>\n<pre><code>输入如下命令：hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d\n</code></pre><p><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-eaf24669105f7742.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>6、测试访问</p>\n<p>在浏览器输入：https://你得用户名.github.io/</p>\n<h2 id=\"\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"\"></a><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/11634944-7ac45e17bae67bd6.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" alt=\"\"></h2><p>恭喜你已经成功了！</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"hexo网站搭建","slug":"hexo网站搭建","count":2,"path":"api/categories/hexo网站搭建.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo+github搭建网站","slug":"hexo-github搭建网站","count":2,"path":"api/tags/hexo-github搭建网站.json"}]}